{"tid":178492,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"古龍群合俠傳 (Ser5) 幫招生~~~","createTime":"2017-03-29T14:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T06:31:36.000Z","uid":19747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7267e24578ee94798940cd1b6859ef20e3bce3c","tid":178492,"uid":19747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"大家好, 相信連登都會有玩古龍的巴打。<br />\n想係到邀請各位重玩/新玩既巴打一齊入幫吹水傾計,交流心得.<br />\n<br />\n好記得以前古龍好多幫都有幫聚, 燒野食, 踩單車, 排通宵會場包.<br />\n好多好多既回憶都係古龍到.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟係Ser5 大大話話由1.0斷斷續續玩到宜家, 真係有好多不捨....<br />\n個幫雖然唔多人, 但叫做有個細壇, 歷史都叫悠久, 幫招過百.<br />\n但就係做左咁多年毒撚幫, 開始想邀請大家加入岩岩開放既小組織.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無幫衫, 今係目標就係要大家合力, 官方一出就同心協心搶番黎.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢出錢, 有力出力, 無錢無力就聲援力撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家巴打有心玩既, 小弟一定幫到既就幫, 互相協助, 放心絕無小圈子.<br />\n無論高LV低LV,有冇買包食經升LV, 大家都同心協力. 絕無架子.<br />\n唔會話收左你, 你唔食經就踢走你果D屎忽得野.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有意重玩既巴打就係樓下留個Comment, 我會遂個回覆. 最好就係番個Contact.<br />\n小弟番工係朝9晚5, 我唔係24小時ON, 但見到你係到Comment 過都會主動去Contact你.<br />\n<br />\nCome On~~~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be52735692dbad11bc0f33603e5810592961b9a1","tid":178492,"uid":19747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"推~~~~~~"},{"pid":"82819ee8bdf5fd7ee2f1637db6adea14dd667476","tid":178492,"uid":19747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"推推~"},{"pid":"386135a02af4111f3af8359a164603d65428dae4",